snippet: Missy Franklin held off a hard-charging Federica Pellegrini of Italy to win the 200-meter freestyle, claiming her third victory of the world championships in Barcelona, Spain.
abstract: Missy Franklin wins the 200-meter freestyle, claiming her third victory of the swimming world championships in Barcelona, Spain.
lead_paragraph: Missy Franklin held off a hard-charging Federica Pellegrini of Italy to win the 200-meter freestyle, claiming her third victory of the world championships in Barcelona, Spain.

headline.main: Franklin Wins Third Title at Worlds
